                The Prime Minister (Mr. Churchill)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-07dfea93-7cb6-4256-a5f3-c96f9e25bd2d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
