<p class="">In the event of any application for facilities being received, would it receive sympathetic consideration?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-816d5739-1251-4738-a641-16c4e0c3cbe9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
