            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-d2311c5c-3b68-4254-b5b1-9504c2937f59" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
